        <section>
            <h2>Usage</h2>
            <p>Ocean Club & Resorts is a LLB firm incorporated under the Companies Act, 2022.</p>
            <p><strong>"Applicant"</strong> refers to any individual(s) who are potential vacationers/users applying for membership.</p>
            <p><strong>"Vacationer/User"</strong> denotes the applicant whose membership application has been approved and under whose name the certificate is issued.</p>
            <p><strong>"ANNUAL MAINTENANCE CHARGES"</strong> or <strong>"ANNUAL SUBSCRIPTION FEES"</strong> are payable annually by the vacationer/user.</p>
            <p><strong>"INTERNATIONAL EXCHANGE FEES"</strong> are variable fees required before booking facilities, as mandated.</p>
            <p><strong>"Purple Season"</strong> is from Diwali week through to Christmas and New Year.</p>
            <p><strong>"White Season"</strong> is the rest of the year outside of Purple Season.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>1. Process for Applying</h2>
            <p>Applications must be submitted using the approved format. Membership is subject to Terms and Conditions and Rules and Regulations.</p>
            <p>The Management reserves the right to accept or reject applications without explanation. Corporations may nominate individuals as specified.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>2. Guidelines for Vacationers</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Vacationers may use allocated membership nights each year.</li>
                <li>Rooms are subject to availability. Extra adult charges apply.</li>
                <li>Nights are non-transferable without prior notice.</li>
                <li>Vacationers can stay at allied properties listed on the website.</li>
                <li>Packages are valid only after full payment is received.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>3. Procedure for Using Holiday Benefits</h2>
            <p>Holiday reservations are first-come, first-served, and handled via email or member login. White season members cannot book in purple season.</p>
            <p>Exchange fees for international partnerships apply and vary based on multiple factors.</p>
            <p>Ocean Club & Resorts is not liable for non-fulfillment due to force majeure or external reasons.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>4. Details of Vacationer Packages</h2>
            <p>First users will be prioritized for bookings. Bookings cannot be canceled and count as used once booked. Confirmation is subject to availability.</p>
            <p>Properties may be withdrawn without notice. Additional taxes and levies may apply.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>5. Overall Terms and Conditions</h2>
            <p>Membership and other charges are non-refundable under any circumstances, regardless of usage.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>6. Levies</h2>
            <p>Vacationers are responsible for all applicable taxes. Non-payment results in termination of agreement.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>7. Dispute Resolution</h2>
            <p>Unresolved issues should be escalated to the Ahmedabad resolution team. Disputes are resolved through arbitration under the Arbitration and Conciliation Act, 1996.</p>
        </section>

